author: DarthMunich
title: Brilliant little set
review:
A good example, what Lego could be: Just a few parts, and a whole world can be built. Great fun building and playing. Lego at its best!

Pros:
Nice colour scheme
No special parts
Excellent design

Cons:
None!

author: darthdc
title: Great little set
review:
Got this from the Daily Mirror promotion last year. One of 5 Creator sets given away as part of 12 total.

The Biplane was one of the last to be collected and it proves to be one of the best. Well designed for its size.

Pros

Nice colours
High detail for size

Cons

None
